<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LanguageData>

	<!-- EN: piercing weapons -->
	<PiercingWeapon.label>鼠族穿甲武器</PiercingWeapon.label>
	
	<!-- EN: Craft weapons with increased armor penetration like lances. -->
	<PiercingWeapon.description>提高武器的穿透能力。</PiercingWeapon.description>
	
	
	<!-- EN: mechanical weapons -->
	<MechanicalWeapon.label>鼠族機械武器</MechanicalWeapon.label>
	
	<!-- EN: Craft mechanically-operated weapons such as gunlances. -->
	<MechanicalWeapon.description>可以製造機械武器。</MechanicalWeapon.description>
	
	
	<!-- EN: ballistae -->
	<Ballista.label>鼠族巨型弩炮</Ballista.label>
	
	<!-- EN: Build giant crossbow-like siege weapons capable of being easily operated by Ratkins. -->
	<Ballista.description>研發巨型的彈射武器。就算是身形嬌小的鼠族人也能輕鬆操作。</Ballista.description>


	<!-- EN: advanced ballista bolts -->
	<Advanced_BallistaBolt.label>鼠族先進巨型弩箭</Advanced_BallistaBolt.label>
	
	<!-- EN: Craft more advanced variants of ballista bolt ammunition. -->
	<Advanced_BallistaBolt.description>可以研發出更多種類的弩箭。</Advanced_BallistaBolt.description>
	
	
	<!-- EN: microoptics -->
	<MicroOptical.label>鼠族微光學</MicroOptical.label>
	
	<!-- EN: Reverse-engineer human optics into miniature optical components used in Ratkin sniper rifles, allowing Ratkins to compensate for their species' innately-poor eyesight.\n\nRequires a Ratkin scientist wearing Ratkin glasses to research. -->
	<MicroOptical.description>模仿人類的光學設備。重新為鼠族們專門設計，因為他們的視力很差。</MicroOptical.description>
	
	
	<!-- EN: flechette bullets -->
	<FlechetteBullet.label>鼠族飛鏢彈</FlechetteBullet.label>
	
	<!-- EN: Adapt Ratkin crossbow bolts for use in Ratkin firearms, allowing improved armor penetration at the cost of increased weight.\n\nRequires a Ratkin scientist wearing Ratkin glasses to research. -->
	<FlechetteBullet.description>將鼠族使用的箭頭運用在射擊武器上。鼠族的射擊用弩箭在設計上雖然有點重，但可以穿透厚厚的盔甲。\n\n需要用鼠族眼鏡進行研究。</FlechetteBullet.description>
	
	
	<!-- EN: pulse tech -->
	<PulseTech.label>鼠族脈衝技術</PulseTech.label>
	
	<!-- EN: Integrate pulse technology into various weapons and equipment.\n\nRequires a Ratkin scientist wearing Ratkin glasses to research. -->
	<PulseTech.description>研究如何把脈衝技術應用到武器設備上。\n\n需要用鼠族眼鏡進行研究。</PulseTech.description>
	
	
	<!-- EN: Ratkin apparel -->
	<RatkinClothing.label>鼠族服飾</RatkinClothing.label>
	
	<!-- EN: Tailor various dresses, outfits and accessories for practical everyday wear by Ratkins. -->
	<RatkinClothing.description>鼠族設計的衣服易於穿著。製作專業方便的服裝。</RatkinClothing.description>
	
	
	<!-- EN: High-class Ratkin apparel -->
	<HighClassClothing.label>鼠族高貴服飾</HighClassClothing.label>
	
	<!-- EN: Tailor high-quality antique-styled dresses, outfits and accessories befitting the upper echelons of Ratkin society - diplomats, military, priests, nobility and royalty.\n\nRequires a Ratkin scientist wearing Ratkin glasses to research. -->
	<HighClassClothing.description>高貴的傳統服飾。用作於戰爭與外交上。\n\n需要用鼠族眼鏡進行研究。</HighClassClothing.description>

</LanguageData>